    },
    {
      "locale": "zhCN",
      "text": "“你就这么把他扔在这儿？简直是禽兽不如。”",
      "modification_date": "2026-04-14T10:07:12.6653250Z",
      "translated_from": "enGB",
      "translation_date": "2026-04-14T10:07:12.6653251Z",
      "original_text": "\"And you left him like this? That's monstrous.\"",
      "traits": [
        {
          "trait": "Translated",
          "trait_date": "2026-04-14T10:07:12.6653257Z",
          "locale_text": "“你就这么把他扔在这儿？简直是禽兽不如。”"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "locale": "frFR",
      "text": "« Vous l'avez laissé dans cet état ? C'est monstrueux. »",
      "modification_date": "2026-04-15T08:02:36.4186676Z",
      "translated_from": "enGB",
      "translation_date": "2026-04-15T08:02:36.4186677Z",
      "original_text": "\"And you left him like this? That's monstrous.\"",
      "traits": [
        {
          "trait": "Translated",
          "trait_date": "2026-04-15T08:02:36.4186685Z",
          "locale_text": "« Vous l'avez laissé dans cet état ? C'est monstrueux. »"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "locale": "trTR",
      "text": "\"Onu bu şekilde mi bıraktın? Canavarlık bu.\"",
      "modification_date": "2026-04-16T13:26:26.7758721Z",
